                        <interp inst="t18450512-1201-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 16.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18450512-1201-punishment-156" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18450512-1201-punishment-156" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1201-18450512 t18450512-1201-punishment-156"></join>Transported for Ten Years</rs>. Before Mr. Justice Coltman.</hi>
               </p>
